.TH getwstr 3
.SH NAME
\*Lgetwstr\*O, \*Lgetnwstr\*O, \*Lmvgetwstr\*O, \*Lmvgetnwstr\*O, \*Lmvwgetwstr\*O, \*Lmvwgetnwstr\*O, \*Lwgetwstr\*O, \*Lwgetnwstr\*O  \- Read wchar_t character strings from curses terminal keyboard
.SH LIBRARY
.PP
The \*Lcurses\*O library (\*Llibcurses.so\*O, \*Llibcurses.a\*O)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
.sS
\*L#include <curses.h>\*O
.PP
\*Lint getwstr( wchar_t \(**\*Vwstr \*L);
.PP
\*Lint getnwstr(
.br
        wchar_t \(**\*Vwstr\*L,
.br
        int \*Vn \*L);\*O
.PP
\*Lint mvgetwstr(
.br
        int \*Vy\*L,
.br
        int \*Vx\*L,
.br
        wchar_t \(**\*Vwstr \*L);\*O
.PP
\*Lint mvgetnwstr(
.br
        int \*Vy\*L,
.br
        int \*Vx\*L,
.br
        wchar_t \(**\*Vwstr\*L,
.br
        int \*Vn \*L);\*O
.PP
\*Lint mvwgetwstr(
.br
        WINDOW \(**\*Vwin\*L,
.br
        int \*Vy\*L,
.br
        int \*Vx\*L,
.br
        wchar_t \(**\*Vwstr \*L);\*O
.PP
\*Lint mvwgetnwstr(
.br
        WINDOW \(**\*Vwin\*L,
.br
        int \*Vy\*L,
.br
